
<h2>How to grade</h2>
<% if current_user.experimental_condition == "verify" %>
<p>Evaluation consists of two steps. In the first, <strong>assessment</strong> step, you'll grade four of your classmates (per question). In the next <strong>verification</strong> step, you'll then look at eight assessments, as graded by your classmates, and verify that they are correct. </p>

<p>Your answers will go through a similar two step evaluation process. When this evaluation completes, you'll be able to see your grades on this page, and on the Coursera class site</p>
<% elsif current_user.experimental_condition == "identify" %>
<p>You'll grade four of your classmates (per question). For each question, we provide you a set of common correct and wrong answers to help you assess.</p>

<p>Your answers will go through a similar evaluation process. When this evaluation completes, you'll be able to see your grades on this page, and on the Coursera class site</p>
<% else %>
<p>You'll grade four of your classmates (per question). For each question, we provide you a set of common correct and wrong answers to help you assess.</p>

<p>Your answers will go through a similar evaluation process. When this evaluation completes, you'll be able to see your grades on this page, and on the Coursera class site</p>
<% end -%>
<div class="divider">Your assessments</div>

<% @questions.each do |q| %>
<table class="table table-hover">
<thead><tr><th>Question</th><th>Status</th><th>Actions</th></tr> </thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td><%= q.title %></td>
<% finished_evaluations = @completed_identifications_by_question[q.id].nil? ? 0 : @completed_identifications_by_question[q.id] 
	finished_verifications = @completed_verifications_by_question[q.id].nil? ? 0: @completed_verifications_by_question[q.id]
%>
<% if current_user.experimental_condition == "verify" %>
<td>You need to assess <%= (4- finished_evaluations)>0 ? (4- finished_evaluations) : 0 %> classmates, and verify <%= (8- finished_verifications)>0 ? (8- finished_verifications) : 0 %>  assessments</td>

<% elsif current_user.experimental_condition == "identify" %>
<td>You need to assess <%= (4- finished_evaluations)>0 ? (4- finished_evaluations) : 0 %> classmates.</td>
<% else %>
<td>You need to assess <%= (4- finished_evaluations)>0 ? (4- finished_evaluations) : 0 %> classmates.</td>
<% end %>
<td>

<% if current_user.experimental_condition == "verify" %>
	<% if finished_evaluations < 4 %>
		<%= link_to "Grade now", grade_identification_path(q.id) %> 
	<% elsif finished_verifications < 8 %>
		<%= link_to "Verify assessments", grade_verification_path(q.id) %> 	 
	<% else %>
		<%= link_to "Grade more submissions", grade_identification_path(q.id) %> | <%= link_to "Verify more assessments", grade_verification_path(q.id) %> 	 
 	<% end -%>
<% elsif current_user.experimental_condition == "identify" %>
	<% if finished_evaluations < 4 %>
		<%= link_to "Grade now", grade_identification_path(q.id) %> 
	<% else %>
		<%= link_to "Grade more submissions", grade_identification_path(q.id) %>
 	<% end -%>
<% else  %>
<!-- baseline -->
	<% if finished_evaluations < 4 %>
		<%= link_to "Grade now", grade_baseline_path(q.id) %> 
	<% else %>
		<%= link_to "Grade more submissions", grade_baseline_path(q.id) %>
 	<% end -%>
<% end -%>
</td>
</tr>

</tbody>

</table>
<% end %>
<div class="divider">Your grades</div>
<p>Your grades are still being computed. Please check back later.</p>